{"tid":652759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"靠食排解寂寥 曼谷動物園猩猩食到癡肥","createTime":"2018-05-04T05:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:12:26.000Z","uid":153228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"137b072db7601f23ec1957962c95fd985d21c974","tid":652759,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180504/58146416?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F58146416%3F&d=k8O58QSgpWBO%2F%2FiQWoKAojACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=ecea57cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F58146416%3F&h=356f0497\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180504/58146416?</a><br />\n<br />\n被困在籠內、生活空間有限、只可以依賴進食來排解寂寥，就是這隻棲息於泰國曼谷動物園內紅毛猩猩的寫照。英國攝影記者拍攝到這隻猩猩不斷伸手到籠外要食物，因而養成癡肥體態，叫人心痛。<br />\n<br />\n現居於印尼婆羅洲（Borneo）的攝影記者及環保分子蓋科斯基（Aaron Gekoski）一直紀錄各大動物園虐待動物的情況，他最近在曼谷一個動物園拍到一隻紅毛猩猩的日常生活，只見牠坐在籠子邊吃完粟米後，就再伸手要求更多食物。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「這隻猩猩很明顯有癡肥問題，牠沒有足夠空間運動，每天不斷被人餵食，這都是籠養猩猩的特徵。」他又指野生紅毛猩猩大多在樹上生活，並會在樹上築巢睡覺，現在只能坐在冰冷地板上等待下一餐。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，蓋科斯基解釋野外的紅毛猩猩都是獨居生活的，現在被拍違背習性，與另外兩隻同類共處，他直言：「籠養動物最主要的問題，是它令動物失去選擇權。」<br />\n他續說：「紅毛猩猩是有智慧和有感知力的動物，需要外間刺激和鍛煉，除了癡肥外，牠明顯無所事事，看起來亦很沮喪，就只是坐在欄杆前咬欄杆，或是一直伸手等待餵食。」蓋科斯基將這攝照片上載至社交網後，已引起網民關注，不少人對紅毛猩猩的處境表示悲傷和憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180503/large/1525321889_5419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180503%2Flarge%2F1525321889_5419.jpg&h=cf980336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/135421_89b1313a6ece46f122af919eed2d1d37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F135421_89b1313a6ece46f122af919eed2d1d37.jpg&h=4720cadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180503/large/1525321893_0b8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180503%2Flarge%2F1525321893_0b8a.jpg&h=87f58003&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"158a6b46dd953a00acae20b6a637e516972cb9ce","tid":652759,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"第二隻🦍唔肯食🌽<br />\n仲難搞"},{"pid":"4f9f1ad26a93b838e85135ee58f1a7baa98693b6","tid":652759,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"第一同第三張唔關事貼出黎做乜"},{"pid":"0776845759dde924c22ea8fefbbcdeec022cd4c6","tid":652759,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9f1ad26a93b838e85135ee58f1a7baa98693b6","tid":652759,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"第一同第三張唔關事貼出黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"對比<br />\n第一同三係正常size<br />\n第二張係癡肥"}]}